# Build context hygiene for the phantom-stack image.
# The Dockerfile copies the whole project; exclude noise and the nested
# duplicate tree so the editable install picks up the real top-level package.
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.pytest_cache
.ruff_cache
.mypy_cache
build
dist
.coverage*
.venv
.env
# Nested duplicated source tree (not the real package layout)
src/sdk-python
# Our own stack dir
phantom-stack
